sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant GetX as GetX Router
    participant Splash as Splash Page
    participant Comment as Comment Page
    participant Controller as CommentController
    participant API as API<br/>(JSONPlaceholder)

    App->>App: Load Environment Config
    Note over App: 🌐 API_URL: https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com
    
    App->>GetX: Initialize GetMaterialController
    Note over GetX: Instance created & initialized
    
    GetX->>Splash: Navigate to /splash
    activate Splash
    Splash->>Splash: Display Splash Screen
    deactivate Splash
    
    Splash->>GetX: Splash Complete
    GetX->>Comment: Navigate to /comment
    
    activate Comment
    Comment->>Controller: Create CommentController
    Controller->>Controller: Initialize
    Controller->>Controller: onReady()
    
    Controller->>API: GET /comments
    activate API
    API-->>Controller: 200 OK (Comments Data)
    deactivate API
    
    Controller->>Comment: Display Comments
    deactivate Comment